@startuml
|Match Management|
start
:Select a field, a date, and a time slot;
:Submit POST /v1/fields/{field_id}/reservations;
|Field Management|
:Check that the field is active;
:Check that times use full-hour or half-hour boundaries;
:Check that duration is 60, 90, or 120 minutes;
:Check that no active overlap exists;
if (Validation OK?) then (yes)
  :Create the reservation;
  :Publish ReservationCreated;
  :Return 201;
else (no)
  :Return 400 or 409;
endif
stop
@enduml
